# =====================================================================
# School-data storage policy (see docs/data_storage_policy.md):
# Database / school data lives in Supabase, NOT in git.
# =====================================================================
# Raw school uploads — Supabase Storage bucket `raw-uploads/{school_id}/`
# Keep local copy for ETL development, but never commit:
data/source/

# Local-only scratch
data/local/
data/exports/

# These ARE committed (transitional, until Tier 1 cutover):
#   data/processed/*.json        — powers the Tier 0 static demo; will be
#                                  replaced by a build-time export from Supabase
#                                  Postgres at Tier 1.
#   demo/data/processed/*.json   — same, duplicate for self-contained demo folder.
# Once Supabase is live and the demo reads from Supabase queries, both move
# out of git too.

# Deliverable artefacts (committed):
#   handover/*.xlsx — the data-handover template we send to schools.

# Superpowers brainstorming companion (visual mockups)
.superpowers/

# PDFs
PDFs/

# Supabase
# .mcp.json

# Conversation log
# conversation.md

